      <title>亨特誓言保守党如果赢得英国大选将减税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/jeremy-hunt-vows-conservatives-will-cut-taxes-if-they-win-uk-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣杰里米·亨特在周五的一次演讲中承诺，如果他的执政保守党获胜，他将在即将到来的英国大选后减少英国税收，他还将重申取消英国国家保险工资税的雄心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/jeremy-hunt-vows-conservatives-will-cut-taxes-if-they-win-uk-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
